---
import { ArrowRightIcon, UserIcon } from "@lucide/astro"
---

<section id="about" class="space-y-6">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-x-4">
    <UserIcon size="20" stroke-width="1.5" />
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">about</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-prose space-y-4 leading-relaxed text-pretty">
    <p class="drop-cap">
      I'm Aryan Kaushik. I study engineering in Delhi, India, and spend most of my free time writing code for projects I actually want to exist.
    </p>

    <p>
      Most of what I build is on the web, in TypeScript, with React, Next.js, and Node.js, whatever the project calls for. I also spend time solving DSA problems and picking up new tech along the way.
    </p>

    <p>
      Curious to know more?,
      <a href="/#contact">
        get in touch
        <ArrowRightIcon size="14" stroke-width="1.5" class="inline" />
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
